metadata.name: MaryJane
metadata.description:
Mary Jane, oh Mary Jane,  
A plant of beauty, so insane,  
With leaves so green and buds so bright,  
Her beauty shines both day and night.

She takes you on a flight so high,  
To realms of peace up in the sky,  
A tempting haze that fills the air,  
With fragrant scents beyond compare.

With every puff, her charm takes hold,  
Her soothing touch, so calm and bold,  
And as she leads you through her maze,  
You'll find your worries set ablaze.

So enjoy her gifts with measured pace,  
And savor every moment of her grace.
